description:
All the Hermits have been busy doing amazing things since Season 11 started... I've been sick, playing with villagers. We manage to get a number of little starter farms going at our base and collect some resources.

Then when I start feeling better, we make the push to get an early Frog Light Farm going so we can get some cool lights for our Cyberpunkish build style. Then we get working on the entrance to Part Mart, the first main entrance into The Complex. I go over some of the Lore for the base and reveal my new skin for Season 11.

Hermitcraft Website: http://www.hermitcraft.com
